original_title: Tell you about: the birds and the bees, sagittarius rising
overview: To the images of awakening spring, a woman talks to a man. She reflects on his actions towards her. Who she was and who she has become. By saying good bye to what once was, she accepts her altered new self. But with anger of what was taken from her, she's determined to seek justice.
title: Tell you about: the birds and the bees, sagittarius rising
